  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aimed to evaluate the safety and symptomatic outcomes achieved with Stapled
      Transanal Rectal Resection (STARR) compared to biofeedback training in patients with
      obstructed defecation syndrome (ODS).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
